  <TITLE>Include filters in Order History Page (public store)</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>As more and more orders are placed by a customer, they are shown all at once without pagination or filtering. I think an admin configurable option should be there so as to display order history page as tabs such as Recent Orders, Previous Orders (before last 6 Months) etc. This will improve the customer experience for shops such as Clothing, Cosmetics, or Grocery where more orders are placed by the same customer and the history page becomes crowded. Source: https://www.nopcommerce.com/en/boards/topic/40944/feature-include-filters-in-order-history-page Source 2: https://www.nopcommerce.com/en/boards/topic/46841/suggestion-allow-customers-to-choose-view-orders-in-a-date-range</DESCRIPTION>
